chat.msg: hola, q tal? ready to go?
okay si, go straight betweeen tiger and butterfly
alright! i'm between the tiger and the butterfly now
where to next?
despues, cross the stick thats infront of the rock and go behind el pajaro
sure thing, crossed the stick and now behind the parrot
what's next, buddy?
go around the bird and under, and cross the 2grey rocks and one black rock
okay, went around the bird, under and across the rocks
now i'm near that frog. what now?
go a little bit staight pass the light green tree but under the frog, and then stop when you past the frog
got it, just passed the frog, chilling under this tree now
what do we do next?
not make a u-turn and head back towards the alligator
can do! made a u-turn and headed back toward the alligator
what's next?
cross it and go foward and cross  black rock and then cross two grey rock
alright, just crossed the alligator, black rock, and two grey rocks
i can see the elephant again. where to now?
now you pass the giraffe and you cross on the sticknear the snake
done and done! i passed the giraffe and crossed the stick near the snake
now go straight to treasure
awesome! went straight and here's the treasure! *finished* what a fun game! ya did great, mate!
hi there! que comience el juego!!
ok, que hago?
¡genial! muevete unos pasos a la izquierda, pasa por debajo de una banca de madera y cruzas esa senda hacia un puesto de flores
no llegues hasta allí, solo da una vuelta en 'u' grande a la izquierda, vuelve a cruzar la senda hacia el adorable perro blanco. ¿lo ves?
ok, estoy al lado del perro blanco
buen trabajo. ahora cruza sobre la rama hacia el sur
continúa hacia abajo en el mapa. encontrarás a otro perro blanco, está junto a un mantel de picnic a cuadros rojo y blanco. ¿lo ves?
si, estoy de frente al perro blanco
excelente, ahora pasa por encima del mantel y sigue hacia el oeste, como rozando el tazón de bayas que verás por ahí
ok
bien hecho, luego verás una rama de madera que cruza un río, vete al norte por ella
okay
genial, ahora al otro lado del riachuelo, hay un arbusto verde, el objetivo es rodearlo por la derecha
así podrás llegar hasta el puesto de flores. ¿me sigues?
okay si
perfecto, ahora gira a tu izquierda y ve por debajo del puesto de flores, te encontrarás con un gran puente con dos personas en bicicleta
sigue pasando al lado de ellos hacia la izquierda
hey!!! ya comenzamos?
okay, go south until you reach the white brown dog
got it! i'm now standing right next to the dog, can see a fire to my right, and what's next buddy?
now keep going straight until you on trail, now go right and keep straight till you reach fire, now go behind fire and around it, then go under mushroom plants and stop
alright, did as you said and now i'm underneath the mushroom plants
i can see a blue car to my south and a blue telescope farther away. what's the next move, mate?
yes, so go right untill you pass the cars hood a little, now them make a u-turn back onto the trail, you will now follow south on trail until you reach the telescope
perfect, i've reached the telescope
i can see some rocks and a house to my west. what's my next step, mate?
hola, q tal? ready to go?
yes
awesome! walk southwest under the first palm tree and do a quick right then left before the third tree
head straight to the south
okay
cool! now, veer left of that cute brown puppy up ahead, then swing right back towards the south
okay got it
great! now, slide between that big rock on your left and the small one on your right till you hit the water
okay I'm in the water
excellent! alright, there's a red crab coming up
swing right by it and brush by that big rock on your left while you flow westwards in the water
okay
nice job! keep going west till you hit a middle-sized rock
next, you're gonna see a shark, don't panic! just sharply turn right
okay
awesome! now, head back towards the land
you'll pass between that last medium rock and a cool tri-colored ball. once clear, start moving to the north
around the ball or?
right past it, buddy! keep it on your right side while the rock remains on your left
okay
now, nudge slightly left and go northwest. you'll be going between a red tent and a larger speaker
keep both on opposite sides. cool stereo, right?
okay
make a nice arc around the tent, then head straight south until you nearly reach the water again
okay
sweet! just before hitting the water, turn right and walk below that red kayak there
okay..
perfect! lastly, turn north
follow the kayak till you bump into a lovely small green bush. and there you have it! smashed it, haven't you?
